5AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=9fd7c5cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n黃大仙區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=1be77d74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n深水埗區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=e2f7ee5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n灣仔區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=5c161f94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話（呢個係每日都可以做既）</span></span></strong><br />\n打電話搵議員(之前有巴打post過出黎，可以自己搵下)問下國慶期間區內有咩最新活動、巴士路線、有咩醫生診所好介紹呀等等，電話打唔通既whatsapp都可以，無whatsapp既巴絲打可以send email去，連email都無既可以fax過去查詢下，無人應既話可以搵下無限fax大法fax到佢應機為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2.連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n都係搵立法會議員/區議員辦事處啦，無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3.裝修</strong></span></span><br />\n有好多議員都扎根起屋邨做左好耐，裡面啲裝修又殘又舊，有心既手足可以襯國慶幫佢地補下油、翻新下添置返少少國慶節日既氣氛，用咩色就自己決定啦。<br />\n補充:好多office既出入口好窄，大家入office查詢既時候動作唔好太大呀，唔小心撞到佢地d玻璃就大鑊喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>4.餵office既龜龜食野(蟲系魔法師出動)</strong></span></span><br />\n巴絲打們都可以準備少少紅蟲、蚯蚓、生雞蛋、甜野呀個d比入面既龜龜食，可以吸引到更多蟲蟲輕易大量繁殖既就更好。大家知啦，議員們公事繁忙，萬一無時間餵佢地，龜龜都仲有少少野食丫嘛。<br />\n補充：拉開櫃桶餵既時候記住小心啲，唔好倒瀉手上罐可樂呀，會惹到成地蟻架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原post:</strong></span><br />\n國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e7d023200f716bd6db667cec4eb4066f96e479","tid":1606792,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"029f4e308163a2e045b7d248d7050e18de20314c","tid":1606792,"uid":271056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:02:38.000Z","msg":"機場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:19:18.000Z","msg":"不相認"},{"pid":"5514a7d37e069a4e9d422853e97169dbdd698a47","tid":1606792,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3808c2280143b93c4a46bf471656171cb05712b1","tid":1606792,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41690d281305f562389180aefc397bae6369473","tid":1606792,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f